flowchart TD
    A[Start standalone command/exec control stream] --> B[tty=true size=80x24]
    B --> C[Process emits marker R + SIZE1:80x24]
    C --> D[send command/exec/resize 100x40]
    D --> E[Process gets SIGWINCH]
    E --> F[Process emits marker W + SIZE2:100x40]
    F --> G[send write+closeStdin PING]
    G --> H[Process emits READ:PING]
    H --> I[result exit 0]
    I --> J[proof stays outside transcript contour]
